OL,7,Finjured man, who has been taken to
OL,8,Fhospital, on suspicion of aggravated
OL,9,Fburglary.
OL,11,FA third man has been arrested on
OL,12,Fsuspicion of murder and attempted
OL,13,Fmurder.
OL,15,FTwo police cordons are in place at two
OL,16,Fhouses in Eccles Road and will remain
