OL,3,CMan found dead and another injured
OL,4,Cafter suspected burglary
OL,6,FDivisional Commander Chief
OL,7,FSuperintendent Dave Kirby, said: "This
OL,8,Fis an understandably concerning
OL,9,Fincident for this small rural
OL,10,Fcommunity.
OL,12,F"However, while we are in the early
OL,13,Fstages of the investigation, we
OL,14,Fbelieve this is a targeted incident.
OL,16,F"Residents will see an increased
OL,17,Fpolice presence as enquiries continue
OL,18,Fand we will give further updates as
OL,19,Fsoon as possible.
